snippet: Tanaka, who missed two and a half months last season, threw for 34 minutes on level ground in his first workout of the year at the Yankees’ minor league complex in Tampa.
abstract: New York Yankees pitcher Masahiro Tanaka throws in his first workout of 2015 at team's minor league complex in Florida.
